Super inexpensive, trendy fashion.
I always say that one should not spend a lot of money on trends.
And GlamSquadShop allows local fashionistas to look on-trend without spending a fortune.
Don't let the Junior-y and club girl styles deter you.
I'm pushing 40 and even I can find sleek, chic pieces that are totally age appropriate.
The best piece of advice I can give you is to sign up for the store's email newsletter.
You'll be the first to know of new arrivals, including the super cute items that sell out fast.
Keep this boutique on your shopping radar at all times.

